        {'instr':'Open `m365.cloud.microsoft/chat` > **Notebook** tab > **+ New Notebook**. Add the listed reference files, then paste the prompt below.', 'prompt':'Add 3 sources: /RT_01_Store_Performance.xlsx, /RT_02_Store_Operations_Manual.docx, /RT_05_Halal_Compliance_Register.docx. Set the Instruction: \'You are my governance reviewer. Identify contradictions across the 3 sources and present concise pre-reads for the Board.\' Then ask the Notebook to identify where the network performance narrative, the operations manual, and the halal compliance obligations are misaligned ahead of the Investment Committee. Request a concise answer with 3 sections: Contradictions to Resolve, Questions Directors Will Ask, and Recommended Pre-Reads, all with citation to the source file.'}
